	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I've been wondering about this for a while. This may be a dumb question to some of you, but it's an interesting subject. Is it possible to make your own mappers with their own capabilities? If so, how come more homebrew mappers haven't been made? Or have they been? Sorry, this question has never really been answered directly to me, and I'm just curious.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
